Class RepastAntiInflammatoryCytokine

java.lang.Object
prkmodel.types.templates.AbstractNervousSystemElement

prkmodel.repast.RepastAntiInflammatoryCytokine
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cytokine<Neuron>, MoveableNervousSystemElement, NervousSystemElement
public class RepastAntiInflammatoryCytokine extends DefaultAntiInflammatoryCytokine
Extends the functionality of DefaultAntiInflammatoryCytokine to integrate with the Repast Simphony framework. Represents an anti-inflammatory cytokine in the simulation that interacts with neurons.

    • RepastAntiInflammatoryCytokine

      public RepastAntiInflammatoryCytokine(Neuron target, Microglia parentMicroglia, int lifespan, double x, double y, double z)
      Constructs a new RepastAntiInflammatoryCytokine with the specified target neuron, parent microglia, lifespan, and position.
      Parameters:
      target - the target neuron for this cytokine
      parentMicroglia - the parent microglia that produced this cytokine
      lifespan - the lifespan of this cytokine
      x - the X coordinate of the cytokine
      y - the Y coordinate of the cytokine
      z - the Z coordinate of the cytokine
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - if the target or parent microglia is null
      IllegalArgumentException - if the coordinates are invalid
